content:
Route Calls to a Queue

To route calls in a phone channel, edit the contact center channel, and specify the routing method and queue for the channel.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud

From Setup, enter Voice, select Amazon Contact Centers or Partner Telephony Contact Centers, open and edit the contact center.
 
In the Routing Type field, select Queue, and then select the queue. Click Save.
title: Routing Calls with Service Cloud
